              <h2>Recommended starting points</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Superfat:</strong> 5% for general body bars, 3% for
                  laundry soap, 7–8% for extra conditioning facial bars.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Water : lye ratio:</strong> 2.3–2.7 for most cold
                  process recipes.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Lye concentration:</strong> 30–33% for a good balance
                  of workability and cure time.
                </li>
              </ul>

